videos.description: Lashann Higgs creates a turnover and then gets the bucket with her left hand for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Higgs steals and scores for Texas

videos.description: AJ Alix makes a jumper in the final seconds of the first half to make it a one-point game at halftime vs. No. 8 Texas.
videos.headline: Alix's jumper gives Florida St. momentum before half

videos.description: Alecia Sutton quickly drives down the court and kicks the ball out to Brooke McCarty, who makes the 3-pointer to extend Texas' lead.
videos.headline: McCarty sinks corner 3-pointer for Texas

videos.description: Brooke McCarty drives down the court and bounces a pass to Audrey-Ann Caron-Goudreau who makes the basket for Texas.
videos.headline: McCarty uses nice pass to set up bucket

videos.description: Brooke McCarty intercepts a pass and finishes with a lay-in, giving her 24 points vs. Tennessee.
videos.headline: McCarty reaches 24 points with layup
